The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Timothy J. Walton, Appellant. [733 NYS2d 663]

—Judgment

unanimously affirmed. Counsel’s motion to be relieved of assignment granted (see, People v Crawford, 71 AD2d 38). (Appeal from Judgment of Ontario County Court, Henry, Jr., J. — Burglary, 3rd Degree.) Present — Pigott, Jr., P. J., Hayes, Wisner, Kehoe and Burns, JJ.
